    global-layer slice + any normalization), OR re-export/re-train the head with live-path K, so
    live wc_scores share the curated reject boundary (ctrl_paris/foreign < s0).
  - B4-v2 admission: gate each capture through the teacher-forced ablation oracle
    (SP_B3_DISPOSER=2, collapse < TAU=-8) so only load-bearing novel facts are consolidated
    (also stops the question-turn self-capture).

